 effect. Cover and freeze for at least 3 hours or overnight."},{"content":"Remove semifreddo from the freezer, reverse into a serving plate and garnish with reserved chopped pistachio nuts, roasted sesame seeds and pomegranate seeds. Refrigerate until soft enough to slice and serve."}],"hintsAndTricks":["Use 100 % natural coconut cream; coconut cream that has emulsifying agents added may cause the mixture to separate into creamy and watery layers.","Do not prolong the freezing time or the coconut cream will become difficult to handle."],"basicInfo":["easy","10m","4h 10m","10 portions"]}